<plot>Too Soon for Sorry explores the cultural and economic conditions behind the prison industrial complex through a look at four US Prisons. Desire and fear, adventure and greed, control and revenge have created not only a highly sophisticated form of oppression with 2 million people behind bars but a deadly mix for a whole generation of African Americans and Latinos.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?612712</url></doc>
